quran[6{c,v,t}:
16,88,jin logon ne khud kufar ki raah ikhtiyar ki aur dosaron ko Allah ki raah se roka inhen hum azaab par azaab den ge uss fasaad ke badlay jo woh duniya mein barpaa karte rahay
16,89,"( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, aِnhin uss din se khabardaar kar do ) jab ke hum har ummat mein khud usi ke andar se aik gawah utha khara karen ge jo uss ke muqablay mein shahadat day ga, aur inn logon ke muqablay mein shahadat dainay ke liye hum tumhe layein ge aur ( yeh isi shahadat ki tayari hai ke ) hum ne yeh kitaab tum par nazil kar di hai jo har cheez ki saaf saaf wazahat karne wali hai aur hadaayat o rehmat aur basharat hai unn logon ke liye jinhon ne sir tasleem khham kar diya hai"
16,90,Allah Adal aur ahsaan aur sila rehmi ka hukum deta hai aur badi o be hiyai aur zulm o zayad-ti se mana karta hai woh tumhe nasiyaat karta hai taakay tum sabaq lau
16,91,"Allah ke ehad ko poora karo jabkay tum ne is se koi ehad baandha ho, aur apni kasmain pukhta karne ke baad toar nah daalo jabkay tum Allah ko apne oopar gawah bana chuke ho Allah tumahray sab af-aal se bakhabar hai"
16,92,"tumhari haalat uss aurat ki si nah ho jaye jis ne aap hi mehnat se soot kata aur phir aap hi usay tukre tukre kar dala tum apni qasmon ko aapas ke mamlaat mein makr o fraib ka hathyaar banatay ho taakay aik qoum doosri qoum se barh kar faiday haasil kere halan ke Allah is ehad o Paiman ke zareya se tum ko azmaish mein dalta hai, aur zaroor woh qayamat ke roz tumahray tamam ikhtilafat ki haqeeqat tum par khol day ga"
16,93,"agar Allah ki Mushiyat yeh hoti ( ke tum mein koi ikhtilaaf nah ho ) to woh tum sab ko aik hi ummat bana deta, magar woh jisay chahta hai gumraahi mein dalta hai aur jisay chahta hai raah raast dikha deta hai, aur zaroor tum se tumahray aamaal ki baz purse ho kar rahay gi"
